info.name: GoodReads Dark Sans Background Book-Stack
info.description: Background book-stack graphic for GoodReads Dark Sans style.
info.additionalInfo: This "style" only contains the book-stack graphic that appears on the left side of GoodReads, and is to be used in conjunction with my other style GoodReads Dark Sans. I had to split this out because it was using over half the allotted space of 1k for the style and I was pushing those limits already. I hope this does not inconvenience.
